1
00:00:01,250 --> 00:00:03,419
SERI DRAMA INI ADALAH FIKSI
DAN TAK BERKAITAN

2
00:00:03,544 --> 00:00:05,880
DENGAN TEMPAT, ORANG, ORGANISASI,
DAN KEJADIAN NYATA.

3
00:01:13,030 --> 00:01:15,658
{\an8}KAPAL PESIAR ARA SUNGAI HAN

4
00:01:48,274 --> 00:01:49,483
Pergi ke sana.

5
00:01:50,443 --> 00:01:51,819
Pergi ke sana, sekarang!

6
00:01:53,279 --> 00:01:54,405
Jangan bergerak!

7
00:01:55,323 --> 00:01:58,075
Kau menunggu apa? Cepat bergerak!

8
00:01:59,201 --> 00:02:00,244
Diam saja!

9
00:02:00,536 --> 00:02:01,621
Bergerak!

10
00:02:10,254 --> 00:02:11,255
Cepat bergerak!

11
00:02:15,926 --> 00:02:17,428
Tundukkan kepala! Bergerak!

12
00:02:21,057 --> 00:02:22,141
-Kemari.
-Bergerak!

13
00:02:23,976 --> 00:02:25,061
Tetap di sana!

14
00:02:25,478 --> 00:02:26,479
Tetap menunduk!

15
00:02:26,687 --> 00:02:27,938
-Menunduk!
-Bergerak!

16
00:02:28,022 --> 00:02:29,482
-Tetap menunduk!
-Bergerak!

17
00:02:29,565 --> 00:02:31,317
-Cepat bergerak!
-Tetap diam!

18
00:02:31,442 --> 00:02:33,069
Bergerak! Masuk ke sana!

19
00:02:33,152 --> 00:02:34,153
Turun!

20
00:02:38,074 --> 00:02:40,868
-Tetap menunduk!
-Bergerak lebih cepat!

21
00:02:41,077 --> 00:02:42,578
Ayo cepat!

22
00:02:43,579 --> 00:02:46,624
Kami butuh bantuan. Kapal dibajak
oleh orang bersenjata…

23
00:02:46,707 --> 00:02:47,750
Tutup teleponnya.

24
00:02:52,713 --> 00:02:54,507
-Keluarkan dia.
-Baik, Pak.

25
00:03:04,058 --> 00:03:05,184
Tetap menunduk!

26
00:03:07,770 --> 00:03:08,813
Tetap menunduk!

27
00:03:21,242 --> 00:03:22,660
-Menunduk!
-Tetap menunduk!

28
00:03:31,377 --> 00:03:33,504
-Kami mendarat di kapal!
-Ayo bergerak!

29
00:04:06,787 --> 00:04:09,540
KAPAL PESIAR ARA SUNGAI HAN

30
00:04:20,384 --> 00:04:21,427
Aku menyerah!

31
00:04:29,059 --> 00:04:30,436
-Aman.
-Aman.

32
00:04:31,103 --> 00:04:33,939
-Aman.
-Target telah dilumpuhkan.

33
00:04:34,023 --> 00:04:35,232
<i>Tak ada korban sipil.</i>

34
00:04:49,997 --> 00:04:52,458
Perahu itu kenapa? Itu menuju ke sini.

35
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,668
-Bukan milik kita.
-Siapa?

36
00:05:05,596 --> 00:05:06,680
Lindungi para tamu!

37
00:05:13,312 --> 00:05:15,022
Astaga.

38
00:05:19,401 --> 00:05:20,903
Sial!

39
00:05:22,154 --> 00:05:24,281
Sial, ini sakit.

40
00:05:24,824 --> 00:05:27,159
Kau tak dengar aku bilang, "Aku menyerah"?

41
00:05:27,368 --> 00:05:28,994
Itu kau, Sersan Han?

42
00:05:30,454 --> 00:05:32,665
-Kau bagus pakai itu.
-Jangan menyeringai.

43
00:05:32,790 --> 00:05:33,791
Atau kubunuh kau.

44
00:05:34,166 --> 00:05:35,167
Kau belum berubah.

45
00:05:35,918 --> 00:05:38,170
Tapi kau tampak lemah sebagai polisi.

46
00:05:38,754 --> 00:05:41,590
Makanya kau memerankan penjahat di sini.

47
00:05:42,049 --> 00:05:44,009
Kurasa karier gemilangmu berakhir, Han.

48
00:05:46,428 --> 00:05:48,097
-Dasar berengsek…
-Sial kau.

49
00:05:49,223 --> 00:05:50,641
Dasar berengsek!

50
00:06:07,449 --> 00:06:09,577
Kau kira Polisi Sungai Han penurut?

51
00:06:22,381 --> 00:06:24,216
-Cukup!
-Kenapa?

52
00:06:24,592 --> 00:06:26,510
Kau lihat mereka mengajakku berkelahi!

53
00:06:26,635 --> 00:06:28,846
Kita sedang latihan sekarang.

54
00:06:30,097 --> 00:06:32,057
Apa peranmu? Teroris, bukan?

55
00:06:32,683 --> 00:06:34,810
Kau mestinya tahu
kapan berhenti dan ditangkap.

56
00:06:34,894 --> 00:06:36,395
Itu akan buat petinggi senang.

57
00:06:36,979 --> 00:06:38,272
Astaga, sakit sekali.

58
00:06:39,398 --> 00:06:40,441
Kau juga!

59
00:06:40,816 --> 00:06:45,154
Dia marah karena kau tetap menembaknya
meski dia menyerah.

60
00:06:45,696 --> 00:06:47,865
Bagaimanapun, aku minta maaf untuknya.

61
00:06:47,948 --> 00:06:50,367
-Maafkan aku. Jangan marah.
-Tak apa.

62
00:06:51,744 --> 00:06:52,995
Sialan.

63
00:06:54,246 --> 00:06:56,373
-Apa katamu?
-"Sialan"?

64
00:06:56,916 --> 00:07:00,252
Kau dengar dia memaki, bukan?
Dia baru saja bilang, "Sialan."

65
00:07:01,128 --> 00:07:02,171
Hei.

66
00:07:02,338 --> 00:07:03,881
Beri aku pistolnya.

67
00:07:04,173 --> 00:07:05,424
Ini, ambillah.

68
00:07:06,133 --> 00:07:08,052
Ambillah.

69
00:07:10,429 --> 00:07:12,473
-Berengsek kau!
-Sialan!

70
00:07:12,723 --> 00:07:14,099
Berhenti!

71
00:07:14,266 --> 00:07:15,809
Sialan, kalian berengsek.

72
00:07:16,977 --> 00:07:19,188
-Jisoo, hentikan mereka.
-Baik, Pak.

73
00:07:19,939 --> 00:07:21,774
Sersan Han! Tolong berhenti…

74
00:07:21,899 --> 00:07:23,651
Sialan! Kemarilah!

75
00:07:23,734 --> 00:07:25,694
Ayo lawan aku, Berengsek!

76
00:07:26,946 --> 00:07:29,615
Kami melindungi Sungai Han,
dasar berengsek!

77
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:30,741
Segera hentikan

78
00:07:30,824 --> 00:07:32,660
Proyek Pengembangan Sungai Han
yang tak etis!

79
00:07:32,743 --> 00:07:34,662
KAMI TOLAK
EKSPANSI BISNIS KAPAL PESIAR

80
00:07:35,579 --> 00:07:37,331
Segera hentikan

81
00:07:37,915 --> 00:07:39,917
ekspansi bisnis kapal pesiar!

82
00:07:41,669 --> 00:07:44,505
-Kubilang awas.
-Segera hentikan

83
00:07:44,672 --> 00:07:46,674
Proyek Pengembangan Sungai Han
yang tak etis!

84
00:07:46,799 --> 00:07:48,676
Segera hentikan…

85
00:07:48,801 --> 00:07:50,844
-Apa?
-…ekspansi bisnis kapal pesiar.

86
00:08:01,647 --> 00:08:02,731
Ada apa?

87
00:08:07,277 --> 00:08:09,488
-Lepaskan aku.
-Pak, mohon tenang!

88
00:08:09,613 --> 00:08:11,532
Lepaskan! Oke! Aku akan jalan sendiri.

89
00:08:11,907 --> 00:08:13,033
{\an8}Kubilang aku jalan!

90
00:08:13,784 --> 00:08:15,119
{\an8}-Ayo! Cepat!
-Ayo!

91
00:08:15,995 --> 00:08:17,705
-Kau ini kenapa?
-Lepaskan aku.

92
00:08:17,788 --> 00:08:19,999
Kalian menyakiti bahuku.

93
00:08:20,082 --> 00:08:21,250
Bahuku!

94
00:08:21,417 --> 00:08:22,626
GARIS POLISI

95
00:08:23,377 --> 00:08:24,628
Bicara di kantor polisi.

96
00:08:25,170 --> 00:08:26,171
Aku tak mau!

97
00:08:45,232 --> 00:08:46,358
Sialan!

98
00:08:50,112 --> 00:08:51,113
Awas!

99
00:09:06,879 --> 00:09:07,963
{\an8}KEPOLISIAN SUNGAI HAN

100
00:09:08,088 --> 00:09:09,089
{\an8}Hei!

101
00:09:09,673 --> 00:09:11,592
Kuminta kalian memerankan teroris,

102
00:09:11,717 --> 00:09:13,761
bukan teroris sungguhan.

103
00:09:14,136 --> 00:09:15,179
Sersan Han.

104
00:09:15,804 --> 00:09:17,931
Kenapa kau lakukan ini padaku?

105
00:09:18,057 --> 00:09:19,099
Katakan!

106
00:09:20,684 --> 00:09:22,770
Tim SWAT tadi benar-benar menembakku!

107
00:09:22,853 --> 00:09:25,355
Astaga. Bisa kalian percaya si Bodoh ini?

108
00:09:25,606 --> 00:09:27,524
Itu latihan simulasi.

109
00:09:27,733 --> 00:09:29,902
Mereka boleh menembakkan peluru karet.

110
00:09:30,027 --> 00:09:31,236
Itu sangat sakit! Lihat.

111
00:09:31,361 --> 00:09:33,572
Lihat di sini. Chunseok juga kena dan…

112
00:09:34,406 --> 00:09:36,742
-Aku tak apa.
-Dia bilang tak apa.

113
00:09:37,034 --> 00:09:38,035
Katamu sakit.

114
00:09:38,577 --> 00:09:42,247
Bahkan stasiun penyiaran
datang meliput latihan,

115
00:09:42,456 --> 00:09:45,709
lalu kalian sendiri mempermalukan
keseluruhan pasukan polisi.

116
00:09:45,793 --> 00:09:47,002
Kalian senang sekarang?

117
00:09:47,127 --> 00:09:49,379
Bukankah kalian polisi juga?

118
00:09:50,714 --> 00:09:52,091
Kita Polisi Sungai Han, ya?

119
00:09:52,591 --> 00:09:54,468
Ya, kita Polisi Sungai Han.

120
00:09:54,593 --> 00:09:57,554
Lalu kenapa hanya peran tambahan
di latihan di Sungai Han?

121
00:09:58,305 --> 00:09:59,848
Itu salah dan menyedihkan.

122
00:09:59,973 --> 00:10:01,517
Bukankah Sungai Han area kita?

123
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:03,102
Beraninya kau naikkan suaramu!

124
00:10:05,020 --> 00:10:06,438
Kau membantahku?

125
00:10:06,980 --> 00:10:08,732
Aku juga kecewa padamu, Pak Kepala.

126
00:10:09,066 --> 00:10:10,442
Itu latihan di Sungai Han.

127
00:10:10,567 --> 00:10:13,987
Kenapa mereka mau Polisi Sungai Han
berperan sebagai teroris?

128
00:10:14,488 --> 00:10:16,198
Bahkan jika diminta Kantor Pusat,

129
00:10:16,281 --> 00:10:19,284
kau bisa bilang, "Maaf, timku
layak dapat yang lebih baik!"

130
00:10:19,368 --> 00:10:22,204
-Kau seharusnya membela kami!
-Membela kalian?

131
00:10:22,830 --> 00:10:23,872
Pak Kepala, tenang.

132
00:10:23,956 --> 00:10:27,251
Dia menghirup banyak asap,
jadi, dia meracau sekarang.

133
00:10:27,626 --> 00:10:29,670
Ya, sepertinya begitu.

134
00:10:29,753 --> 00:10:32,548
Bawa Berandal ini pergi
sebelum dia membuatku lebih marah.

135
00:10:32,631 --> 00:10:35,509
Ya, Pak. Kami akan pergi berpatroli
agar kau tenang.

136
00:10:35,843 --> 00:10:37,427
-Siap, beri hormat.
-Hormat!

137
00:10:37,511 --> 00:10:39,388
-Terserah. Keluar saja.
-Sungai Han!

138
00:10:43,058 --> 00:10:44,059
Keluar!

139
00:10:50,774 --> 00:10:53,443
Aku tak tahu apakah aku
petugas Polisi Sungai Han

140
00:10:53,527 --> 00:10:54,945
atau pembersih Sungai Han.

141
00:10:55,070 --> 00:10:57,614
Kita lakukan ini
karena kau buat kita dalam masalah.

142
00:10:59,783 --> 00:11:00,951
Yang benar saja.

143
00:11:01,577 --> 00:11:04,288
Astaga, punggungku sakit. Ini melelahkan.

144
00:11:05,038 --> 00:11:07,207
-Jisoo, kau tak apa?
-Tolong!

145
00:11:07,916 --> 00:11:09,209
Kakiku tersangkut!

146
00:11:13,297 --> 00:11:14,298
Kita bunuh saja dia?

147
00:11:14,506 --> 00:11:15,966
Cepat bantu dia.

148
00:11:16,300 --> 00:11:17,759
Tolong aku!

149
00:11:19,511 --> 00:11:21,054
Aku punya bawahan yang lemah.

150
00:11:21,263 --> 00:11:23,056
-Ini tanganku. Apa?
-Terima kasih.

151
00:11:24,641 --> 00:11:26,393
Kubilang aku tak bercanda!

152
00:11:27,060 --> 00:11:28,854
Kalian berdua menyebalkan.

153
00:11:28,937 --> 00:11:30,147
Tak bisa keluarkan dia.

154
00:11:30,522 --> 00:11:31,648
Coba merangkak keluar.

155
00:11:33,066 --> 00:11:35,027
Chunseok, cepat bantu! Aku tersangkut!

156
00:11:35,110 --> 00:11:36,820
Kau harus merangkak sejak awal.

157
00:11:36,945 --> 00:11:38,530
Itu sulit setelah tersangkut.

158
00:11:38,614 --> 00:11:40,365
Astaga.

159
00:11:40,949 --> 00:11:42,075
Ini sangat memalukan.

160
00:11:42,409 --> 00:11:43,535
Pergi!

161
00:11:43,619 --> 00:11:45,120
Hei, lambaikan tanganmu.

162
00:11:45,204 --> 00:11:48,457
Kami Polisi Sungai Han yang melindungi
kebersihan Sungai Han.

163
00:11:49,041 --> 00:11:50,125
Bersenang-senanglah!

164
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:52,628
-Lanjutkan.
-Terus jalan.

165
00:11:57,758 --> 00:12:02,095
Kalian benar-benar kacau. Astaga.

166
00:12:02,221 --> 00:12:04,431
Itu terlihat berbahaya. Kenapa yacht itu?

167
00:12:08,644 --> 00:12:11,188
Sersan Han yang budiman
takkan membiarkan itu, 'kan?

168
00:12:11,271 --> 00:12:12,898
Ayo pergi dan jaga sungai tetap aman.

169
00:12:12,981 --> 00:12:14,441
-Ayo beraksi!
-Ayo!

170
00:12:14,524 --> 00:12:15,609
-Ayo!
-Baik.

171
00:12:16,693 --> 00:12:17,736
Cepat!

172
00:12:23,575 --> 00:12:26,078
KEPOLISIAN SUNGAI HAN
KEPOLISIAN SEOUL

173
00:12:39,841 --> 00:12:41,176
Apa? Kenapa tak berhenti?

174
00:12:41,510 --> 00:12:42,970
-Chunseok, mendekat.
-Oke.

175
00:12:46,181 --> 00:12:48,433
Yacht <i>Kyle! </i>Hentikan yacht kalian.

176
00:12:49,184 --> 00:12:51,687
Berhenti! <i>Kyle!</i>

177
00:12:54,147 --> 00:12:55,315
Sialan.

178
00:12:55,857 --> 00:12:57,025
Mereka tak berhenti.

179
00:12:58,193 --> 00:12:59,444
Chunseok, halangi mereka.

180
00:13:09,371 --> 00:13:12,416
-Kenapa tak kau hentikan?
-Jangan berani menyentuhnya.

181
00:13:14,835 --> 00:13:16,086
Mereka berhenti.

182
00:13:18,880 --> 00:13:20,299
-Mereka sedang apa?
-Lihat?

183
00:13:20,424 --> 00:13:22,134
Mereka tersangkut di jaring ikan.

184
00:13:23,593 --> 00:13:25,887
-Bagaimana kau tahu?
-Saat ini musim belut.

185
00:13:28,557 --> 00:13:30,225
Kau memang petugas veteran.

186
00:13:37,399 --> 00:13:39,776
Hei, Jisoo. Potong jaring ikan
di belakangnya.

187
00:13:39,860 --> 00:13:42,404
Jangan. Mereka tersangkut
karena mereka mau kabur.

188
00:13:42,612 --> 00:13:43,655
Jadi, untuk apa?

189
00:13:44,239 --> 00:13:47,409
Pekerjaan kita menumpas kejahatan
dan melayani publik.

190
00:13:47,576 --> 00:13:49,703
Jika mereka komplain, Pak Kepala mengamuk.

191
00:13:50,162 --> 00:13:52,164
Polisi di industri pelayanan sekarang?

192
00:13:52,289 --> 00:13:53,749
Ya, kau tak tahu itu?

193
00:13:54,166 --> 00:13:56,460
Pekerjaan utama kita untuk melayani.

194
00:13:56,543 --> 00:13:57,544
Hei.

195
00:13:57,961 --> 00:14:00,380
-Kau sedang apa?
-Kau minta aku potong jaring.

196
00:14:02,174 --> 00:14:04,301
Nyalakan mesin dan potong. Ke mana bajumu?

197
00:14:04,426 --> 00:14:05,886
Pakai bajumu!

198
00:14:06,261 --> 00:14:08,347
-Hei, periksa mereka.
-Oke.

199
00:14:15,604 --> 00:14:17,981
Permisi. Kami Polisi Sungai Han.

200
00:14:18,106 --> 00:14:20,442
{\an8}Kalian pasti buru-buru. Kalian mengebut.

201
00:14:20,567 --> 00:14:21,818
{\an8}Itu berbahaya.

202
00:14:23,070 --> 00:14:24,154
{\an8}-Tampan.
-Polisi?

203
00:14:24,237 --> 00:14:25,322
{\an8}Kau benar.

204
00:14:25,447 --> 00:14:28,408
Tapi kenapa kau mengejar kami seperti itu?
Kau menakutiku.

205
00:14:28,950 --> 00:14:31,453
Bahkan yacht ini berhenti
karena ketakutan.

206
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,622
Mereka bilang kapal ini mahal.

207
00:14:33,997 --> 00:14:35,082
Sialan!

208
00:14:36,333 --> 00:14:38,043
Aku harus komplain atas kerusakan.

209
00:14:38,418 --> 00:14:40,879
Terserah padamu. Bisa lihat surat izinmu?

210
00:14:42,005 --> 00:14:43,423
Apa aku seperti nakhoda?

211
00:14:43,548 --> 00:14:45,092
-Ya.
-Salah. Tunggu.

212
00:14:45,509 --> 00:14:46,510
Bukan.

213
00:14:47,803 --> 00:14:49,846
{\an8}Sayang, kemarilah.

214
00:14:49,971 --> 00:14:51,765
{\an8}Kurasa kau belum melihatnya. Lihat.

215
00:14:51,890 --> 00:14:53,266
{\an8}Dia yang mengemudi.

216
00:14:53,767 --> 00:14:56,061
Apa katamu? Dia ingin lihat surat izinmu.

217
00:14:56,144 --> 00:14:57,396
Dia tahu kau mengemudi.

218
00:14:57,479 --> 00:14:58,730
Kalian tampak tak peduli.

219
00:14:58,814 --> 00:15:01,650
Tapi aku sibuk,
jadi, berikan surat izin kalian berdua.

220
00:15:02,275 --> 00:15:04,319
Pak Polisi ingin surat izinmu.

221
00:15:04,653 --> 00:15:06,196
Tapi bukan aku yang mengemudi.

222
00:15:06,863 --> 00:15:09,574
Bukan aku juga, Pak Polisi.

223
00:15:17,582 --> 00:15:19,418
Lihat dia malu.

224
00:15:22,129 --> 00:15:23,505
-Minumlah bersama.
-Ayo.

225
00:15:24,923 --> 00:15:26,883
-Ayo minum bersama.
-Astaga.

226
00:15:28,385 --> 00:15:29,594
Kau mau ke mana?

227
00:15:29,678 --> 00:15:31,638
Astaga, kalian mabuk.

228
00:15:31,721 --> 00:15:33,807
Keselamatan Aktivitas Pelayaran melarang

229
00:15:33,932 --> 00:15:35,559
mengemudi dalam keadaan mabuk.

230
00:15:35,642 --> 00:15:38,478
Kau bisa didenda lima juta won
atau dipenjara setahun…

231
00:15:38,687 --> 00:15:40,063
Kau membosankan.

232
00:15:40,188 --> 00:15:42,357
Ayolah berpesta bersama kami…

233
00:15:46,486 --> 00:15:48,905
-Tangannya sangat cepat!
-Hebat sekali.

234
00:15:49,114 --> 00:15:50,157
-Sersan Han.
-Ya.

235
00:15:50,282 --> 00:15:51,908
-Kita harus pergi.
-Oke.

236
00:15:51,992 --> 00:15:53,660
Kami pergi. Direktur Go.

237
00:15:53,952 --> 00:15:56,872
Ini pemberitahuan biaya penaltimu.
Harap bayar tepat waktu.

238
00:15:56,955 --> 00:15:58,707
Kau akan didenda jika telat bayar.

239
00:15:58,832 --> 00:16:01,084
Jangan mengemudi. Sampai nanti.
Sungai Han!

240
00:16:01,334 --> 00:16:02,711
Taruh minumanmu.

241
00:16:02,794 --> 00:16:05,297
Kau mau ke mana, Pak Polisi?

242
00:16:05,881 --> 00:16:08,967
Bersenang-senanglah, <i>Kyle.</i>

243
00:16:11,011 --> 00:16:13,388
Jika kita biarkan, apa mereka akan kabur?

244
00:16:13,472 --> 00:16:14,723
Mereka tak bisa pergi.

245
00:16:19,394 --> 00:16:20,479
Kunciku…

246
00:16:20,979 --> 00:16:22,564
Kuambil kuncinya.

247
00:16:22,647 --> 00:16:24,065
Kita tim yang hebat.

248
00:16:26,651 --> 00:16:27,944
{\an8}KEPOLISIAN SUNGAI HAN

249
00:16:33,325 --> 00:16:36,453
HAN RIVER POLICE

250
00:17:12,822 --> 00:17:15,575
Keadaan sangat kacau kemarin.

251
00:17:15,951 --> 00:17:18,411
Polisi bahkan tak bisa bekerja sama.

252
00:17:20,705 --> 00:17:22,624
Kukira kau bicara soal protesnya.

253
00:17:22,832 --> 00:17:24,167
Kau membuatku kaget.

254
00:17:25,210 --> 00:17:28,255
Aku minta maaf soal itu, Pemimpin Hwang.

255
00:17:28,755 --> 00:17:30,840
Tak perlu. Itu tak apa.

256
00:17:31,299 --> 00:17:32,384
Omong-omong,

257
00:17:33,051 --> 00:17:35,720
soal kepala desa nelayan itu,

258
00:17:35,804 --> 00:17:37,305
kau harus mengendalikannya.

259
00:17:37,764 --> 00:17:40,809
Kau tak mau ada rumor saat merilis
sebuah bisnis baru.

260
00:17:41,226 --> 00:17:44,187
Menjaga citra yang baik itu penting,
kau tahu.

261
00:17:45,105 --> 00:17:48,191
Ya, Pak. Aku akan lebih memerhatikan
soal itu.

262
00:17:50,151 --> 00:17:51,319
Tapi sejujurnya,

263
00:17:52,028 --> 00:17:53,863
aku cukup terkejut.

264
00:17:54,656 --> 00:17:57,784
-Oleh apa?
-Rutenya bahkan tak menguntungkan,

265
00:17:58,451 --> 00:18:00,662
tapi kau mau tambah
kapal pesiar lebih besar.

266
00:18:03,999 --> 00:18:06,251
Aku hanya mengikuti
rencana besar wali kota.

267
00:18:06,543 --> 00:18:09,004
"Kebangkitan Sungai Han".
"Garis Hidup Seoul".

268
00:18:09,254 --> 00:18:11,506
Apa jadinya Sungai Han tanpa kapal pesiar?

269
00:18:11,965 --> 00:18:14,259
Kami harus pertahankan
meski keuangan sulit.

270
00:18:14,426 --> 00:18:15,468
Berkat kau,

271
00:18:15,594 --> 00:18:18,597
anggaran kota digunakan
untuk mengikis dasar sungai.

272
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:22,309
Agar kapal pesiar besarmu
bisa berlayar tanpa masalah.

273
00:18:24,185 --> 00:18:27,439
Kudengar kau dapat hak bisnis
ke Kota Pertama Sungai Han juga.

274
00:18:27,731 --> 00:18:30,483
Pada titik ini, semua bisnis
yang melibatkan Sungai Han

275
00:18:30,609 --> 00:18:33,403
akan jatuh ke tanganmu, Pemimpin Hwang.

276
00:18:35,238 --> 00:18:37,365
Tapi kudengar

277
00:18:37,449 --> 00:18:40,535
biaya akuisisi dan kompensasi
untuk daratan

278
00:18:40,619 --> 00:18:42,454
cukup besar.

279
00:18:42,537 --> 00:18:44,039
Apa itu takkan masalah?

280
00:18:45,165 --> 00:18:47,417
Jika pengembangannya tertunda,

281
00:18:47,500 --> 00:18:49,502
kita takkan bisa memastikan

282
00:18:50,045 --> 00:18:51,546
masa jabatan ketiga wali kota.

283
00:18:52,130 --> 00:18:54,215
-Kau tahu soal itu, 'kan?
-Tentu.

284
00:18:55,050 --> 00:18:56,718
Kalian tak perlu cemas.

285
00:18:57,469 --> 00:19:00,889
Dengan dukungan dari kalian berdua,
semua akan berjalan lancar.

286
00:19:00,972 --> 00:19:02,307
Ini baru permulaan.

287
00:19:02,641 --> 00:19:03,683
Tentu.

288
00:19:03,767 --> 00:19:06,811
Bagaimana tak kami dukung
saat kau traktir makanan enak ini?

289
00:19:09,689 --> 00:19:10,940
Traktir?

290
00:19:12,359 --> 00:19:14,152
Undang-undang antikorupsi sedang ketat,

291
00:19:14,444 --> 00:19:16,071
jadi, kita bayar masing-masing.

292
00:19:23,161 --> 00:19:24,162
Direktur Go.

293
00:19:25,580 --> 00:19:26,665
Direktur Go!

294
00:20:04,494 --> 00:20:05,745
Silakan buka.

295
00:20:21,928 --> 00:20:23,096
Alih-alih makanan ini,

296
00:20:23,888 --> 00:20:27,434
harap terima hadiah yang tak bisa
dilacak ini sebagai terima kasihku.

297
00:20:28,977 --> 00:20:30,061
Pemimpin Hwang.

298
00:20:30,770 --> 00:20:33,064
Kau menggoda kami.

299
00:20:33,732 --> 00:20:36,109
Ya, benar. Aku benar-benar tertipu.

300
00:20:41,614 --> 00:20:43,241
Wah, lihat ini!

301
00:21:21,237 --> 00:21:22,822
Keparat.

302
00:21:23,948 --> 00:21:25,283
Aku tak pernah bayangkan

303
00:21:25,366 --> 00:21:27,452
aku masih merendahkan diri setua ini.

304
00:21:28,077 --> 00:21:29,204
Dengar.

305
00:21:29,287 --> 00:21:31,331
Jangan seperti aku saat seusiaku.

306
00:21:31,915 --> 00:21:34,000
Itu mengerikan.

307
00:21:34,250 --> 00:21:37,253
Bagaimana jika kuambil alih
agar kau bisa istirahat…

308
00:21:39,339 --> 00:21:41,174
Maksudmu aku harus pergi sekarang?

309
00:21:42,467 --> 00:21:43,551
Kau mau posisiku?

310
00:21:43,676 --> 00:21:46,262
Tidak, maksudku kau bisa
bersantai sedikit…

311
00:21:48,056 --> 00:21:49,224
Maafkan aku, Pak.

312
00:21:50,850 --> 00:21:52,101
Dasar bodoh.

313
00:21:52,519 --> 00:21:54,896
Aku biarkan kau mengikutiku
karena kau keluarga.

314
00:21:57,315 --> 00:21:59,526
-Kau kira posisi ini milikmu?
-Maaf, Paman.

315
00:21:59,943 --> 00:22:01,444
Lagi-lagi bilang begitu! Sial.

316
00:22:09,077 --> 00:22:11,162
-Maaf, Pak Pemimpin.
-Sialan!

317
00:22:15,834 --> 00:22:18,795
Beri uang pada bajingan
yang berdemo di kapal.

318
00:22:18,878 --> 00:22:21,923
Pastikan aku tak melihatnya lagi. Paham?

319
00:22:22,090 --> 00:22:23,091
Ya, Pak.

320
00:22:50,869 --> 00:22:53,413
Kenapa salah untuk memanggilnya paman,
siapa dia?

321
00:22:53,538 --> 00:22:54,789
Kenapa tak boleh?

322
00:22:54,914 --> 00:22:57,834
"Lagi-lagi bilang begitu"? Apanya?

323
00:23:01,296 --> 00:23:02,964
Suaranya juga sangat keras.

324
00:23:03,923 --> 00:23:05,758
Aku hampir mengompol. Sial.

325
00:23:11,347 --> 00:23:12,891
Aku mau makan makanan hangat.

326
00:23:23,484 --> 00:23:25,236
{\an8}KEPOLISIAN SUNGAI HAN

327
00:23:25,570 --> 00:23:26,946
Itu bau sekali.

328
00:23:27,280 --> 00:23:29,866
Hei, kenapa kau tak keringkan
baju renangku?

329
00:23:30,491 --> 00:23:31,951
Kau tak jemur milikmu?

330
00:23:32,327 --> 00:23:33,620
Cuacanya cerah kemarin.

331
00:23:34,078 --> 00:23:35,830
Astaga, kau sangat egois.

332
00:23:36,664 --> 00:23:37,707
Merapikan bajumu?

333
00:23:37,916 --> 00:23:39,500
Sekalian punyaku juga.

334
00:23:43,296 --> 00:23:46,007
Baju renangmu sangat kering dan harum.
Harum pewangi.

335
00:23:46,090 --> 00:23:48,051
Itu karena keringatku tak bau.

336
00:23:49,177 --> 00:23:51,721
Kau tak pernah menyelam,
jadi, tak berkeringat.

337
00:23:51,888 --> 00:23:55,183
Apa ada cara untuk menghindar
dari menyelam hari ini?

338
00:23:55,266 --> 00:23:56,935
Maksudmu? Kita akan bebas tugas.

339
00:23:57,727 --> 00:23:59,687
Ada latihan hari ini.

340
00:24:00,104 --> 00:24:02,231
Sungguh? Aku tak ingat mendengarnya.

341
00:24:02,815 --> 00:24:05,485
Berkat kau, kita harus ikut
sesi latihan disiplin.

342
00:24:07,070 --> 00:24:11,074
Ya, kita juga dihukum, padahal hanya kau
yang pantas mendapatkannya.

343
00:24:11,324 --> 00:24:12,784
Kita tim, bukan?

344
00:24:13,117 --> 00:24:14,869
Kita harus berlatih bersama.

345
00:24:15,244 --> 00:24:18,206
Aku tak mau. Bisa bolos saja?

346
00:24:19,248 --> 00:24:20,375
Tidak, tak bisa.

347
00:24:20,833 --> 00:24:22,001
-Sungai Han.
-Ya.

348
00:24:22,251 --> 00:24:24,295
-Sungai Han.
-Pergi ke pusat pelatihan.

349
00:24:25,630 --> 00:24:27,548
-Jangan berani bolos.
-Baik.

350
00:24:30,301 --> 00:24:32,136
Aku tak mau dikelilingi oleh pria.

351
00:24:32,804 --> 00:24:35,723
Ada wanita. Kopral Do Nahee
dari Divisi Patroli Yichon.

352
00:24:36,099 --> 00:24:39,102
Dia bukan wanita.
Dia pernah menjadi tentara.

353
00:24:50,780 --> 00:24:52,407
PUSAT AKUATIK POLISI SUNGAI HAN

354
00:24:53,366 --> 00:24:56,536
Apa Kopral Do sungguh tentara?

355
00:24:57,328 --> 00:24:59,872
Dia di Angkatan Laut.
Penangkap Hantu, kau tahu?

356
00:25:13,511 --> 00:25:14,804
Mencolok seperti biasa.

357
00:25:16,097 --> 00:25:17,223
Sersan Han.

358
00:25:19,100 --> 00:25:20,935
Ada apa denganmu? Apa kau gila?

359
00:25:21,060 --> 00:25:22,729
Aku muak pakai baju renang hitam.

360
00:25:23,104 --> 00:25:24,814
Jadi, bagaimana penampilanku?

361
00:25:25,023 --> 00:25:27,275
-Kau tampak cantik.
-Terima kasih.

362
00:25:27,859 --> 00:25:29,193
Angkatan Laut pakai merah.

363
00:25:32,655 --> 00:25:34,032
Semuanya, berkumpul!

364
00:25:34,449 --> 00:25:36,784
Baiklah.
Kulihat kalian sudah berlatih keras.

365
00:25:39,495 --> 00:25:40,830
Hei, Do Nahee!

366
00:25:40,997 --> 00:25:44,459
Baju renangmu terlalu…

367
00:25:44,542 --> 00:25:46,919
Bukankah warna merah terlalu mencolok?

368
00:25:47,295 --> 00:25:48,588
Ini hanya baju renang.

369
00:25:48,713 --> 00:25:50,214
Tidak.

370
00:25:50,298 --> 00:25:52,508
Lain kali, pastikan pakai hitam

371
00:25:52,759 --> 00:25:54,302
dan naikkan ritsletingnya!

372
00:25:56,846 --> 00:25:59,307
Omong-omong,

373
00:25:59,432 --> 00:26:02,393
pasti melelahkan bagi kalian
untuk latihan seperti ini

374
00:26:02,477 --> 00:26:04,729
setelah bekerja seharian hari ini.

375
00:26:04,812 --> 00:26:05,897
-Benar?
-Ya.

376
00:26:06,522 --> 00:26:08,649
Pastikan berterima kasih pada Sersan Han

377
00:26:08,858 --> 00:26:12,361
karena memberikan kesempatan latihan ini.

378
00:26:14,906 --> 00:26:17,658
Tapi membosankan berlatih
tanpa hadiah, bukan?

379
00:26:17,784 --> 00:26:19,118
Bagaimana jika ada lomba

380
00:26:19,660 --> 00:26:22,872
dan divisi patroli yang menang
diizinkan untuk tak ikut

381
00:26:22,997 --> 00:26:25,166
latihan berikutnya? Apa pendapat kalian?

382
00:26:25,291 --> 00:26:26,584
Itu hebat!

383
00:26:28,628 --> 00:26:30,588
-Chunseok.
-Ya, Pak?

384
00:26:30,755 --> 00:26:33,174
-Kau tak ikut berlatih?
-Aku latihan.

385
00:26:33,299 --> 00:26:35,009
Tapi rambutmu benar-benar kering.

386
00:26:35,551 --> 00:26:37,929
-Sudah kering.
-Apa rambutmu antiair?

387
00:26:38,554 --> 00:26:40,056
-Berhenti bermalasan.
-Baik.

388
00:26:40,473 --> 00:26:41,557
Omong-omong,

389
00:26:41,974 --> 00:26:43,142
lakukan yang terbaik!

390
00:26:43,267 --> 00:26:44,560
-Baik, Pak.
-Baiklah.

391
00:26:51,484 --> 00:26:52,527
Hei.

392
00:26:59,784 --> 00:27:02,620
-Ada misi penting untukmu.
-Apa itu?

393
00:27:04,413 --> 00:27:06,624
Pria ini sangat sensitif.

394
00:27:07,792 --> 00:27:09,418
Dia mudah geli.

395
00:27:09,585 --> 00:27:12,296
Kau mau aku curang? Aku tak mau.

396
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:14,799
Itu bukan curang, tapi mengatur strategi.

397
00:27:15,091 --> 00:27:16,217
Akan kubelikan belut.

398
00:27:16,300 --> 00:27:17,677
Air tawar, bukan laut.

399
00:27:17,802 --> 00:27:19,428
Akan kubelikan yang air tawar.

400
00:27:19,637 --> 00:27:20,972
Ayo bermain.

401
00:27:22,265 --> 00:27:24,058
Baik, bersiaplah!

402
00:28:00,386 --> 00:28:01,762
Lihat cepatnya dia keluar.

403
00:28:01,846 --> 00:28:03,472
-Akan kutunjukkan caranya.
-Ya.

404
00:28:04,348 --> 00:28:06,434
Hanya itu kemampuanmu? Astaga.

405
00:28:25,995 --> 00:28:27,580
Infeksi telingaku memburuk!

406
00:28:27,663 --> 00:28:29,332
Baiklah, naik saja.

407
00:28:33,252 --> 00:28:34,754
-Kau bercanda?
-Apa?

408
00:28:57,985 --> 00:29:00,321
Hei, infeksi telingaku memburuk.

409
00:29:00,404 --> 00:29:02,573
Kau sedang apa? Kau buat aku gelitiki dia.

410
00:29:02,657 --> 00:29:05,284
Kau memarahiku saat aku sedang kesakitan?

411
00:29:05,868 --> 00:29:06,911
Astaga…

412
00:29:43,990 --> 00:29:45,241
-Chunseok.
-Ya?

413
00:29:45,366 --> 00:29:46,951
Kita harus tarik Sersan Han.

414
00:29:47,076 --> 00:29:49,370
Kompetisi tetap kompetisi.
Biarkan saja dia.

415
00:29:50,663 --> 00:29:52,498
Kopral Do mungkin pingsan sekarang.

416
00:29:52,790 --> 00:29:54,250
Tak apa, biarkan saja mereka.

417
00:30:38,169 --> 00:30:39,754
-Kau aman?
-Nahee, tak apa?

418
00:30:40,588 --> 00:30:42,506
-Lepaskan kacamatanya!
-Bawa ke sini.

419
00:30:43,215 --> 00:30:44,300
Astaga, ini gila.

420
00:30:47,511 --> 00:30:49,180
Apa yang kau lakukan? Kau gila?

421
00:30:49,305 --> 00:30:50,348
Sialan.

422
00:30:57,313 --> 00:30:59,815
Nahee! Kau tak apa?

423
00:31:03,819 --> 00:31:06,238
Ini hanya permainan, tak perlu berlebihan.

424
00:31:06,947 --> 00:31:08,908
-Kau tak apa?
-Berapa skornya?

425
00:31:09,241 --> 00:31:10,576
Berapa skornya?

426
00:31:13,496 --> 00:31:17,458
Lihat kau, Nahee. Kau hampir mati.

427
00:31:17,583 --> 00:31:19,877
Kau pasti berusaha keras.

428
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:22,922
Divisi Patroli Yichon
memenangkan lomba ini!

429
00:31:23,047 --> 00:31:24,965
-Selamat.
-Hore!

430
00:31:27,009 --> 00:31:28,135
Astaga.

431
00:31:28,969 --> 00:31:31,097
Aku harus apa dengan badut itu?

432
00:31:31,180 --> 00:31:32,431
Kita menang!

433
00:31:32,765 --> 00:31:35,476
Lihat orang aneh itu.
Aku menyesal menyelamatkannya.

434
00:31:36,977 --> 00:31:37,978
Hei…

435
00:31:38,813 --> 00:31:40,981
-Apa kau masuk ke air?
-Ya.

436
00:31:42,983 --> 00:31:44,151
Itu benar, Pak.

437
00:32:00,418 --> 00:32:01,836
Anak baru?

438
00:32:03,838 --> 00:32:05,881
Tak juga. Kau bekerja tiga bulan, ya?

439
00:32:06,006 --> 00:32:07,091
Ya, Pak.

440
00:32:07,174 --> 00:32:10,136
Kukira pesta penyambutan
selalu di tempat kami. Sedihnya.

441
00:32:11,303 --> 00:32:12,430
Dia tak bisa minum.

442
00:32:12,930 --> 00:32:15,433
Kenapa kau datang hari ini
meski tak bisa minum?

443
00:32:16,058 --> 00:32:19,854
Aku ingin makan bersama kalian
dan juga minum.

444
00:32:20,062 --> 00:32:23,357
Letnan Lee bilang mau membelikanku belut
jika kukalahkan lawanku.

445
00:32:25,651 --> 00:32:28,571
Chunseok, kenapa kau,
seorang petugas Polisi Sungai Han,

446
00:32:28,654 --> 00:32:30,865
sangat membenci latihan? Keluar saja!

447
00:32:30,948 --> 00:32:34,368
Bekerja di departemen lain mengerikan.
Aku suka di sini.

448
00:32:34,535 --> 00:32:36,245
Jam kerja kita normal.

449
00:32:36,454 --> 00:32:37,705
Selain itu,…

450
00:32:37,788 --> 00:32:39,498
aku bisa menikmati malamku.

451
00:32:39,582 --> 00:32:42,084
Apa kau tahu betapa indahnya Sungai Han?

452
00:32:42,710 --> 00:32:44,962
Ada banyak kota dengan sungai di dunia.

453
00:32:45,087 --> 00:32:46,422
-Makan.
-Tapi tak ada

454
00:32:46,547 --> 00:32:48,048
yang seindah sungai kita.

455
00:32:48,174 --> 00:32:49,467
-Makan.
-Malamnya indah.

456
00:32:50,092 --> 00:32:51,552
Tamannya juga bagus. Hei.

457
00:32:51,844 --> 00:32:54,763
Kenapa kalian fokus makan
saat aku sedang bicara sekarang?

458
00:32:56,891 --> 00:32:58,142
Halo!

459
00:32:58,476 --> 00:33:00,436
-Aku baru mau pesan ikan.
-Kalian di sini.

460
00:33:00,519 --> 00:33:01,604
Ya, halo.

461
00:33:01,687 --> 00:33:02,771
Hei.

462
00:33:03,022 --> 00:33:04,982
-Kau mau belut lagi?
-Ya.

463
00:33:05,107 --> 00:33:06,358
-Ya.
-Akan kumasak.

464
00:33:10,905 --> 00:33:13,115
Kau makan semua belutnya.

